      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey quick question, i'm flying into heathrow tomorrow and then need to get up to edinburgh. i was thinking of taking the heathrow express to paddington, then catching an lner train from king's cross. how much buffer time should i actually leave between those two to be safe? dont want to miss the train if the tube is slow or something.",
